"Dwarvish Heroes are the strongest, toughest and wisest from the dwarves. "
"Hardened by centuries of warfare under the ground and also above it, their "
"strength and wisdom grew beyond measure. Their incredible skill with smithing"
" granted them the mightiest hammers and most solid armours ever, and even "
"dwarvish kings have a strong respect towards them."
