msgid ""
"Great Magi spread rumours that only several mages per century are given the "
"title of a great mage, but the truth is quite different. They are speaking "
"about Elder Magi, and misuse the similarity and the rarity of them. Among "
"them, there is an even sparser number who, despite their blessed age, are "
"more progressive than the younger professional fraternity. Elder Magi are the"
" real masters of magic, the ones who make new spells and truly understand the"
" arcane. Even if they are not trained for battle, their powerful magic can "
"destroy most enemies before the need for quick reflexes comes."
