"Masters of the Assassins are almost always sent to slay their victims rather "
"than to steal something. Their favourite technique is to stab enemies from "
"behind with a dagger, but because not all murders can be done silently, they "
"also practised standard combat, and carry a scythe they can wield with scary "
"skill, that is particularly useful when surrounded. Deadly at night, "
"exterminators are less able fighting under the sun."
msgstr ""

