"Tales are told of the mightiest warriors and generals, who, cursed with hate "
"and stung by betrayal, have experimented with demonic magic and returned back"
" to this world as Infernal Knights. Wielding the same weapons as in life, "
"they command both fire and the Undead in their quest for revenge."
