#: .\units\Knight_of_Magic.cfg:18
#: .\units\Knight_of_Magic.cfg:141
msgid ""
"After heavy practice, sword mages slowly increase the number of pieces of "
"metal they wear, and become more resilient. Also, their combat abilities "
"increase greatly, and become feared for their versatile style of combat. But "
"they can still keep on getting better, and their ambition and pride makes "
"adjacent allies fight worse because of the envy."
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\Knight_of_Magic.cfg:126
