msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=Monstrosity LotI, race=undead
#: .\units\Monstrosity.cfg:21
msgid ""
"When a Walking Corpse kills a victim and reanimates it to unlife, it also "
"drains a part of its soul. This rarely has an effect, but sometimes, when "
"much of the flesh has rotten away already, this accumulated soul energy "
"reshapes the corpse into a horrid, tentaculous form with bones protruding "
"from it that floats around, scaring everything."
msgstr ""

