#. [unit_type], id=Skeletal Dragon LotI, race=undead
#: .\units\Skeletal_Dragon.cfg:25
msgid ""
"Even of the mightiest living creatures there will remain nothing but bones "
"and dark sinew in the end. But dark powers that know no bounds raise also "
"those back to life – and if they are downright nasty in the shape of a "
"harmless looking pile of bone... Only few who have been deceived by that "
"appearance lived long enough to realise their terrible mistake.\n"
"\n"
"Gameplay notes: This unit can learn to use a dark breath that can, along with"
" its jaws, turn this skeletal dragon into a doom to all living.\n"
