"supernatural dexterity in melee combat. Clad in armour of magical metal, that"
" does not burn faerie beings, Elvish Sprites make potent melee combatants and"
" spellcasters in the same person."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=Swordmaster LotI, race=human
#: .\units\Swordmaster.cfg:4
msgid "Swordmaster"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=Swordmaster LotI, race=human
#: .\units\Swordmaster.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Some royal guards show a great expertise with swords, not only good defensive"
" abilities, so they act as the main offensive force of defensive forces. "
"Shattering the lines of enemy defence in times of war and protecting castles "
"in times of peace, swordmasters are the greatest elite of human soldiers.\n"
"\n"
"Note: The ability upgrades may require some books to learn them from."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: .\units\Swordmaster.cfg:43
msgid "two-bladed sword"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=Sword Mage LotI, race=human
