msgid ""
"The Black Army is a company of professional well-paid full-time mercenaries, "
"purely devoted to warfare. Their skill is hard to match, their loyality to "
"gold is endless and their mercy is unheard of. Bowmen of this army are "
"archers with incredibly strong arms, their draw is so forceful that special "
"bows are given to them. Their strength also allows to aim crushing sword "
"strikes, even if their skill with the second weapon is not that great."
