#. [unit_type], id=Dark Dragon, race=monster
#: .\units\enemies\Dark_Dragon.cfg:21
msgid ""
"A dark dragon is a legendary creature, normally seen only in fantastic tales."
" They are very rare, and were it not for the historical events, the "
"singlehanded destruction of cities and towns that these creatures have "
"wrought, they might be dismissed as mere myth. Legends are very specific "
"about the ravages of dark dragons; noting their great strength, speed, their "
"preternatural cunning, and above all else, the great darkness that "
"accumulates inside of them all the time.\n"
"\n"
"Battling a dragon is said to be the pinnacle of danger itself, fit only for "
"fools, or the bravest of knights."
msgstr ""

