"Deathshroom is a venomous mushroom that grows in symbiosis with Flowers of "
"Evil. It feeds on the very essence of evil that exists around it, and "
"channels it to nearby infernal plants, that give it substances it needs to "
"grow."
msgstr ""

#. [regenerate], id=symbiosis 24
