"them down. Nothing will grow for a hundred years wherever their evil feet "
"step. So evil and perverted are the demonologists. Demons are creations of "
"incredibly foul magic and only the worst of the worst unites with them. Even "
"the knowledge of demonology is so strictly forbidden that it is questionable "
