"Darkness. However, this experiment hopelessly failed and demons became evil "
"creatures, so powerful and twisted, that they even forced the Light and "
"Darkness to unite to lock them into a different dimension, into the world of "
"Inferno, with no way out. But their presence in Irdya suggests that somebody "
"knew or figured out how to release them.\n"
"\n"
